{"id": "1244042094528434266", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "在2个支线页面也塞了几句英文，全部都是一模一样的英文装饰，\n最上面是：\nsilver begets knowledge.\n银生知识。\n\n下方是：\nSilver begets knowledge.\nKnowledge beget the key.\n■■■■■■\nThe key leads to reason.\nThe gate sets us free.\n银生知识。\n知识生钥匙。\n这把钥匙通向理性。\n这扇门让我们自由了。\n\n意识潜游和特遣记录一样，只不过没有最后一句The gate sets us free.\n\n→好心守密人翻译润色（包括下方课题）：https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1221527962495484015/1349683992227610644", "timestamp": "2024-05-25T21:39:08.520000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-04-18T06:58:04.785000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1244042094100611092", "filename": "IMG_20240526_051713.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 216556, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1244042094100611092/IMG_20240526_051713.jpg?ex=69cce7bc&is=69cb963c&hm=cae453206878c9d6ead04b19f92106000deeffb0b6c58558dd84aaa1c3d34b3e&"}, {"id": "1244042094331560010", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-26-05-17-38-70_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 183761, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1244042094331560010/Screenshot_2024-05-26-05-17-38-70_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=69cce7bc&is=69cb963c&hm=99f7572e875e28cc5ae26f1d1e36ee2e787a59dd846dbac4f8499c931ec4552a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1244042810869682227", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "以及，从商店界面看课题下面的英文也是这4句，翻来覆去也就这么几句话。", "timestamp": "2024-05-25T21:41:59.309000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1244042810449989753", "filename": "IMG_20240526_051901.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 734282, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1244042810449989753/IMG_20240526_051901.jpg?ex=69cce867&is=69cb96e7&hm=a097066e014ef2d867e9b5769d796f9a9ebacc9f51656d2283f8293ca1f15fcc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1244045407005184172", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "进入课题后，点击左下角时间可以看到完整图片。左上角金色字就是我们的弥萨格大学mythag university.\n\n而右下角有两行花体英文，内容是：\nCall upon us, worthy one,wake us from our slumber.\nWhen the stars are right,when the moon shines bright.\n主啊，求你呼唤我们，把我们从沉睡中唤醒。\n当群星正位，当明月高悬。\n\n~~在此刻怀疑一下，学校是不是被蹈海者占领了。~~", "timestamp": "2024-05-25T21:52:18.276000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-25T21:52:58.405000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1244045406913171558", "filename": "IMG_20240526_054658.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1244501, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1244045406913171558/IMG_20240526_054658.jpg?ex=69ccead2&is=69cb9952&hm=175d320b13a28c0a4438b31b8e71e82221ef76627bc1e85a0ab5d9279e73cfa3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
